displayName: City of the Grasslands, Campus - Home of the Playful Piper Pippa

parameters:
Thief Nora: Thank you so much...! I wonder what would have
happened if I hadn't met Pippa.

Playful Pippa: I'm glad I could be of help. If someone says
it's for the sake of an important friend, I'll lend my
support.

Thief Nora: I'll make sure not to cause any trouble for
everyone. I'll head back to the inn soon. Thank you so
much!
Playful Pippa: I spent quite a bit of money to get that.
Thief Nora: Ah, I'm sorry... If it's about money--

Playful Pippa: Money is not a problem, you know... You
understand the meaning of coming to a man's room this late,
right?
Thief Nora: Eh, hey, please stop touching me!

Playful Pippa: Oops, if you struggle... the honey jar might
break, you know.

Playful Pippa: Don't worry, don't worry! Just leave
everything to me.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
